{"AllowMultiple":false,"Description":"Refactor refreshPaymentPanel() and wirePaymentPanel() to support sidebar inline view toggles and dynamic modal integration for quick cash denominations and split payments.","EndLine":447,"Instruction":"Replace refreshPaymentPanel() and wirePaymentPanel() in features-pos.js to support the new modals and compact sidebar panels","ReplacementContent":"    function refreshPaymentPanel(){
      const totals = RS.getTotals();
      const note = document.getElementById('pay-method-note');
      const checkoutBtn = document.getElementById('btn-checkout');
      if(!checkoutBtn) return;
      document.querySelectorAll('[data-pay-method]').forEach(btn=>btn.classList.toggle('active', btn.dataset.payMethod === paymentState.method));
